name: MOONOPOLI MOON GAME
description: Moonopoli is a game where aliens and astronauts work together to mine minerals the call $MOON for their survival. These are a collection of Launch Portal to summon Gen 0 MOON-citizen NFT for Moonopoli Game in Phase 1. These NFTs can be staked to earn $MOON. The owners of Gen 0 NFT will be airdropped land NFT in Phase 2. In Phase 2, Moonopoli will become a Click-to-Earn P2E game.
